text: Ivica Jelić (28 September 1917 - 17 April 1989) was a Yugoslav gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Yugoslav male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
